check lb dns it redirect to 2 vm or not 

install stress 

#Amazon Linux 2
sudo amazon-linux-extras install epel -y
sudo yum install stress -y


INCREASE CPU LOAD AND CHECK IN "CLOUD WATCH" ----> IN ALARM STATE ( HIGH CPU LOAD) 

load increase command in VM:

dd if=/dev/zero of=/dev/null

it will create the nodes up to maximum mentioned in scaling group 






















